values: My day went good today. Half a day at school. quincy said he was just play about what he said to tiffany. He is ok but yeah. He on the basketball team he not ugly, he nice, he funny, and he closer. But Ge-Man he is a cute, nicer, sweet. I trust Ge-man better than Quincy but he so far away. I don't know.

Today was an exciting day but people get on my nerves. I am starting to believe that i shouldn't be talking to anyone at school no more. It just should be me myself and I. People always trying to mix my words up and i get caught up for no damn reason. I think I gossip because well people tell me stuff and then next thing I know I am repeating what i heard to one of my friends. And then someone always being noisy and repeat what i said but put in words of their own and then say that i said it. Don't nobody in that school really messes with me like that. I am not saying that they scared of me I am saying that I am a nice person and I don't like to argue unless I am playing around or whatever(I argue at home but thats another story). Anyway this bitch tried to slam the door in my face yesterday and I just look at her like what the fuck you think you doing. And I was like I am not going to worry about it because I don't got time for freshmans and left it alone. Because what i look like argruong with a freshman. Anyway she don't like me becuase I don't like what she did to my friend. He really liked this girl and she acted like she liked him to. She was all up on him, always talking to him at his or her locker whatever. And then told everybody they was talking. And then she goes back with her old boyfriend leaving him a cheesy ass note. But you know what thats OK!

Everybody is just being nice to me today. I guess because we got one more week in till winter break comes. i don't know. But it don't matter. Tiffany said that when i talk i don't care what comes out my mouth. But i don't do that all the times do i.  Betty said the same thing. by the way tiffany is my friend and betty is my cousin. I don't know. but i do know i am happy today. i won't let what quincy said bother me. talking about i just want to have sex with her. what in the world made him think i was that type of person. ever since i moved here in NC boys been thinking i am some type of hoe. i don't know why because i am not a loud person or i don't do anything to appear that way. o well. but the only boys who are nice to me are the boys who have girlfriends but are just my friends but they never talk to me when they are around their little girlfriends. like terrance and Barnard. I hate that. thry are cool other days. i don't know. i gotta go. bye.

i am super bored today. yes i love all my friends here but i miss my family. and i didn't blush i cried girl. i miss you so much. and i am praying we come up for christmas. i need your email to so we won't be writing back an forward on this thing. well today was an okay day but it could have een better. i laughed i sang and i cried. what am i to do. i need help. anyway   i keep thinkung about things that i don't want to think about but i will keep those to myself. i don't know you might know what am talking about. i got to go. and it's not fair DC got a snow day on the 7th!!!!!!!!!!!!!

I hate this. i had so much fun in Dc and then we had to come to this boring ass place. My parents teases me. They give me a little taste of fun and then just snatches it away. I miss my cousins my friends and other people. They get on my nerves. When i finish with this semester. i am begging them to let me move to DC with my cousin. I did miss my friends thought but still! Why is my life so boring! My mother and father is the reason. I do nothing but watch tv all day. NC is boring. I am in the middle of nowhere. Somebody help please. I want to have fun today do something. Samone I miss you girl. Ashley Snider and Ashley Stevens I miss yall to. Ashley Snider I am sorry about what I did I still feel really bad about that. i am so sorry.

I feel like a horrible person. I talk to my godsister ex but none of the people who knows seems to care. Well, I care, but just can't stop talking to him because I like him alot. I walked up the street today with my godsister and we ran into HIM! I walked pretending to read a letter. I didn't know what to do. I tried to talk to him but my godsister grabbed my arm and I didn't know what to do. I stood by the pole and he walk by me. He didn't even look at me. I don't know what to do.

Happy Thanksgiving everybody!!! Today is a good day to start my first entry. I am so happy but I hope I will be for the rest of this day. I came down to DC yesterday. I live in NC but I am from DC so don't get yourself all confused. I don't got alot to say because I have a feeling I will have to transform into my quiet and shy mode today because I feel uncomfortable around some of these people. Well I got Samone and Rochelle or Ashley if she comes today. Oh and going to be a good citizen today. I'm going to Feed The HomeLess!! Yes I know clap your hands for me even those who don't know me.
